#: ../../models/voxcpm2.rst:31 c99a0a07e3e543758f1d61ea3cbe75ce
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../models/voxcpm2.rst:33 ac58ddea50c24fdb81ac4395d8d2425e
msgid ""
"VoxCPM 2 is the latest major release — a 2B parameter model trained on 2.36 "
"million hours of multilingual data. It represents a significant leap in "
"capacity, quality, and controllability over the 1.x series."
msgstr ""
"VoxCPM 2 是最新的大版本发布，一个在 236 万小时多语言数据上训练的 2B 参数模型。相较于 1.x "
"系列，它在容量、质量与可控性上都有显著跃升。"

#: ../../models/voxcpm2.rst:35
msgid "Key characteristics:"
msgstr "关键特性："

#: ../../models/voxcpm2.rst:37
msgid "48kHz audio output via AudioVAE V2 (asymmetric 16kHz encode → 48kHz decode)"
msgstr "通过 AudioVAE V2 实现 48kHz 音频输出（非对称 16kHz 编码 → 48kHz 解码）"

#: ../../models/voxcpm2.rst:38
msgid "30-language multilingual support"
msgstr "支持 30 种语言的多语言生成"

#: ../../models/voxcpm2.rst:39
msgid ""
"Voice Design: create a voice from natural-language description, no reference"
" audio needed"
msgstr "Voice Design：通过自然语言描述创建声音，无需参考音频"

#: ../../models/voxcpm2.rst:40
msgid ""
"Style Control: control emotion, pace, and speaking style of a cloned voice "
"via text tags"
msgstr "Style Control：通过文本标签控制克隆声音的情绪、节奏与说话风格"

#: ../../models/voxcpm2.rst:41
msgid ""
"Isolated reference channel for voice cloning (no matching transcript "
"required)"
msgstr "为声音克隆提供隔离式参考通道（无需配套转写文本）"

#: ../../models/voxcpm2.rst:42
msgid ""
"Concat-Projection residual LM fusion and multi-token DiT conditioning for "
"richer expressiveness"
msgstr "Concat-Projection 残差 LM 融合，结合多 token DiT 条件输入，带来更强的表现力"

#: ../../models/voxcpm2.rst:43
msgid "Built on a `MiniCPM-4 <https://github.com/OpenBMB/MiniCPM>`_ backbone"
msgstr "基于 `MiniCPM-4 <https://github.com/OpenBMB/MiniCPM>`_ 骨干构建"

#: ../../models/voxcpm2.rst:45
msgid ""
"Use VoxCPM 2 for all new projects. It is the recommended default for "
"multilingual synthesis, voice cloning, voice design, and production "
"deployment."
msgstr "新项目都建议优先使用 VoxCPM 2。它是多语言合成、声音克隆、Voice Design 和生产部署的默认推荐版本。"

