#: ../../models/voxcpm2.rst:66 9b48ec1203ad41a384fdf9c17f6a81ba
msgid ""
"Design a voice from scratch with natural language descriptions, or control "
"the speaking style of a cloned voice — all through simple text tags."
msgstr "可用自然语言从零设计声线，或用简单文本标签控制克隆声音的说话风格。"

#: ../../models/voxcpm2.rst:74 e9c719b8d4924a93be8f562d82fc3179
