msgstr "**48kHz 音频输出**"

#: ../../models/voxcpm2.rst:79 f1acb38f2b4146c4bc7f8d5b6585460f
msgid ""
"A redesigned AudioVAE V2 with 3x higher upsampling ratio and sample-rate-"
"conditioned decoding produces studio-quality 48kHz audio output."
msgstr "重新设计的 AudioVAE V2 具有 3 倍上采样比与采样率条件化解码，可输出接近录音室品质的 48kHz 音频。"

